25
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:55,040
Wei Zhan,

26
00:01:55,040 --> 00:01:56,160
open the warehouse.

27
00:01:56,440 --> 00:01:57,400
Return the goods to them.

28
00:02:03,360 --> 00:02:04,120
Kudo,

29
00:02:05,520 --> 00:02:07,000
we're old friends after all.

30
00:02:07,600 --> 00:02:09,400
Even if the Chiyan Gang
falls into your hands,

31
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:11,400
