you need to show some sincerity.

37
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:35,600
Is this enough?

38
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:36,800
Mr. Kudo,

39
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:38,600
is Fu Yunzheng sincere enough?

40
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:40,240
Double it and it'll be enough.

41
00:03:26,200 --> 00:03:27,240
The goods have been counted.

42
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:28,800
Take them away.

43
