Load them on the truck.

46
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:14,400
Yes.

47
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:34,400
(Chiyan Gang)
Fu Yunyue,

48
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:36,520
Fu Yunzheng,

49
