how you deceived me over and over again?

51
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:44,160
Today you'll pay the price.

52
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:05,760
Zhiwei!

53
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:20,800
Zhiwei,

54
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:22,760
why are you doing this?

55
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:24,520
Why?

56
00:05:24,520 --> 00:05:25,840
He killed our dad.

57
00:05:25,840 --> 00:05:27,040
He destroyed the Shen family.

58
00:05:29,760 --> 00:05:30,520
Fu Yunzheng,

59
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:33,800
you saved my life back then.

60
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:37,600
So I kept thinking about marrying you.

61
00:05:38,880 --> 00:05:40,080
Now,

62
00:05:40,080 --> 00:05:42,160
whether it's for use

63
00:05:42,160 --> 00:05:43,680
or for love,

64
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:45,800
I'll be your bride.

65
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:49,720
You'll never forget me in this lifetime.

66
00:05:50,378 --> 00:05:53,882
♪Your comings and goings
decide my emotions♪

67
00:05:54,200 --> 00:05:55,280
- Zhiwei.
- Go quickly.

68
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:57,600
- Go now.
- Zhiwei.

69
00:05:57,600 --> 00:05:58,320
Go now.

70
00:05:58,320 --> 00:05:58,960
Zhiwei.

71
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:01,920
(Of course I'm willing to marry you.)

72
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:04,600
(We're the same kind of people.)

73
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:06,840
(I do.)

74
00:06:06,840 --> 00:06:09,594
♪Taking away my love♪

75
00:06:09,760 --> 00:06:13,344
♪Leaving behind a wrecked past♪

76
00:06:13,621 --> 00:06:18,629
♪Eventually, I found solace
in someone else♪

77
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:23,429
♪Everywhere, I see your reflection♪

78
00:06:24,906 --> 00:06:27,024
♪It turns out you are the storm♪

79
00:06:27,184 --> 00:06:33,060
♪It clears up only after you leave♪

80
00:06:33,080 --> 00:06:35,040
Fu Yunzheng, go to hell!

81
00:06:46,320 --> 00:06:47,080
Fu Yunyue,

82
00:06:47,520 --> 00:06:48,840
in life, you're a member of my family.

83
00:06:48,840 --> 00:06:50,040
You'll still be in death.

84
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:54,760
You all go to hell.

85
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:18,240
Kudo,

86
00:07:18,760 --> 00:07:19,680
