87
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:20,880
It's not your place to act wild.

88
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:22,840
Go to hell.

89
00:07:37,400 --> 00:07:38,440
Sir Fu,

90
00:07:41,760 --> 00:07:43,120
I'll give you credit for this.

91
00:07:46,960 --> 00:07:48,560
They might come after us.

92
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:49,440
Let's go.

93
00:08:06,240 --> 00:08:07,240
Useless.

94
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:11,160
Fu Yunyue,

95
00:08:13,440 --> 00:08:15,360
do you think destroying the Shen family

96
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:17,160
will allow you to live happily

97
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:18,760
with Fu Yunzheng forever?

98
00:08:19,200 --> 00:08:20,520
Wishful thinking!

99
00:08:20,520 --> 00:08:22,720
But now I'll reluctantly
fulfill your wish.

100
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:24,960
Go to hell and be a couple there.

101
00:08:27,840 --> 00:08:28,840
Fu Yunyue!

102
00:08:29,080 --> 00:08:29,720
Let's split up.

103
00:08:30,080 --> 00:08:30,920
If you don't come out,

104
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:31,680
I'll distract him.

105
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:32,800
You sneak attack.

106
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:34,520
I'm about to detonate.

107
00:08:35,160 --> 00:08:36,240
Shen Xize wants me.

108
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:38,400
I'll distract him.

109
00:08:38,400 --> 00:08:39,520
No one will survive.

110
00:08:42,320 --> 00:08:44,280
We'll all die together.

111
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:58,760
Fu Yunyue,

112
00:08:59,400 --> 00:09:00,240
if you don't come out,

113
00:09:00,240 --> 00:09:01,520
I'll really detonate.

114
