Fu Yunyue.

118
00:09:16,400 --> 00:09:17,440
If you don't come out,

119
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:19,800
we'll die together.

120
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:34,720
Fu Yunzheng!

121
00:09:35,520 --> 00:09:36,240
Fu Yunzheng!

122
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:36,880
Run!

123
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:37,880
Fu Yunzheng!

124
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:40,440
Go now!

125
00:09:40,720 --> 00:09:42,920
Don't leave me!

126
00:09:43,240 --> 00:09:44,200
I beg you!

127
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:45,320
Fu Yunyue!

128
00:09:48,704 --> 00:09:53,253
♪The four seasons are not
as good as you♪

129
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:58,666
♪I live in the corner of the past♪

130
00:09:58,714 --> 00:10:00,949
♪Slowly understanding loss♪

131
00:10:01,381 --> 00:10:03,712
♪The pure black background♪

132
00:10:03,749 --> 00:10:06,810
♪Convincing myself it has nothing to do
with joy or sorrow♪

133
00:10:07,146 --> 00:10:11,728
♪Later I met someone like you♪

134
00:10:12,256 --> 00:10:15,216
♪But it wasn't you♪

135
00:10:34,060 --> 00:10:38,820
(Two years later)

136
00:10:41,180 --> 00:10:44,020
(Chiyan Gang)

137
00:10:44,440 --> 00:10:45,600
Miss Yue.

138
00:10:48,160 --> 00:10:48,680
Miss Yue,

139
00:10:49,520 --> 00:10:50,680
they still won't confess.

140
00:10:51,040 --> 00:10:52,080
They say they never

141
00:10:52,080 --> 00:10:53,640
smuggled and betrayed the country.

142
00:10:55,000 --> 00:10:55,520
Bring them up.

143
00:11:37,040 --> 00:11:38,640
Messing around on my turf.

144
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:40,720
Do you want to die?

145
00:11:44,040 --> 00:11:44,760
Spare me.

146
00:11:44,760 --> 00:11:45,840
Spare me, I'll never do it again.

147
