149
00:11:48,240 --> 00:11:49,160
Spare me!

150
00:11:49,160 --> 00:11:50,120
Take them away.

151
00:11:50,120 --> 00:11:51,640
Punish according to the gang rules.

152
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:54,160
Spare me, Miss Yue.

153
00:11:54,160 --> 00:11:55,240
Spare me.

154
00:11:56,080 --> 00:11:57,240
Punish one to warn a hundred.

155
00:11:57,240 --> 00:11:58,480
We achieve double the result that way.

156
00:11:59,040 --> 00:12:00,080
From now on,

157
00:12:00,080 --> 00:12:02,320
no one dares to smuggle

158
00:12:02,320 --> 00:12:03,360
on our turf.

159
00:12:04,640 --> 00:12:05,480
Miss Yue,

160
00:12:05,880 --> 00:12:07,880
this matter is finally settled.

161
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:09,040
Today is winter solstice.

162
00:12:09,520 --> 00:12:10,600
Go out and take a walk.

163
00:12:16,320 --> 00:12:17,400
Any news about him?

164
00:12:19,800 --> 00:12:20,800
It's been two years.

165
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:22,640
You...

166
00:12:23,240 --> 00:12:24,360
You should stop waiting for him.

167
00:12:31,760 --> 00:12:33,280
Unless his corpse

168
00:12:33,280 --> 00:12:34,400
is placed in front of me.

169
00:12:35,160 --> 00:12:36,360
I won't accept

170
00:12:36,840 --> 00:12:37,400
this result.

171
00:12:39,066 --> 00:12:41,568
♪Emotions controlled by you♪

172
00:12:41,925 --> 00:12:44,672
♪Begin to turn hysterical♪

173
00:12:46,410 --> 00:12:50,485
♪Unwilling to wake up and to cry♪

174
00:12:51,125 --> 00:12:54,421
♪Unwilling to lose you♪

175
00:12:57,184 --> 00:12:59,439
♪Is it really that easy♪

176
00:12:59,440 --> 00:13:02,272
♪To completely heal you?♪

177
00:13:02,464 --> 00:13:05,339
♪Forget that I once deeply loved you♪

178
00:13:05,340 --> 00:13:08,240
♪Memories etched into my bones♪

179
00:13:08,970 --> 00:13:12,960
♪Those awkward and insincere rejections♪

180
00:13:12,960 --> 00:13:16,602
♪Unable to catch your attention♪

181
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:20,997
♪I get drunk in memories♪

182
00:13:21,066 --> 00:13:23,418
♪You said it's unnecessary♪

183
00:13:23,648 --> 00:13:26,880
♪Everything is because of my impatience♪

184
00:13:28,320 --> 00:13:30,200
(Fu Yunzheng,)

185
00:13:30,880 --> 00:13:33,440
(we promised to grow old together.)

186
00:13:34,200 --> 00:13:35,440
(If you don't come soon,)

187
00:13:36,600 --> 00:13:38,240
(I won't wait for you anymore.)

188
